==English==
===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Pangasinan'''
# a [[region]] of the [[Philippines]] in the island of [[Luzon]]
# a [[province]] of the [[Philippines]] in the island of [[Luzon]]
# a [[language]] of the [[Malayo-Polynesian]] branch of the [[Austronesian]] family of languages spoken in the [[Philippines]], which is the primary language in the province or region of [[Pangasinan]]
# a [[nation]] identified with the region of [[Pangasinan]] and with the [[Pangasinan language]] and culture
# a [[people]] identified with the region, province or nation of [[Pangasinan]] or with the [[Pangasinan language]] and culture
# a [[native speaker]] of the [[Pangasinan language]]
# a [[resident]] or [[inhabitant]] of the province, region or nation of [[Pangasinan]]
# a [[Filipino]] or [[ethnic group]] predominantly of the [[Malay]] race identified with the [[Philippines]] or [[Filipino nation]]
# a ceramic jar or container for storing [[salt]] or salted products
===Adjective===
'''Pangasinan'''
# Pertaining to the people who speak the Pangasinan language and their culture.
